Hey everyone, I could sure use some help finishing off my Sweet Caporal 350-460/30 sub-set. I have been working on it for 3 years now and I am having a hard time finding the final 8 cards. I am looking for the following cards in any condition as long as they would score a numbered grade from PSA. I will happily Buy or trade.

***Sweet Caporal 350-460/30***

Mordecai Brown Chicago
Tim Jordan Brooklyn, Batting
George McQuillan with Bat
George MUllin with Bat
Overall hand Face level
Pfeister Throwing
Wagner, Bat on right shoulder
Wilhelm with bat

Thanks in advance
Isaac

All of these are considered to be Sweet Caporal 350-460/30 "no prints" there are a few of each of them but they are scraps and wouldn't/shouldn't get a number grade from any of the grading company's. PSA has graded a number of them with an A grade.

Here's a thread about a large group of them that sold on ebay
[url]https://www.net54baseball.com/showthread.php?t=208327&highlight=no+prints[/url]

I have a few of the no prints that came from the ebay seller in the above link I posted.
